## 6. Plugin Stack — Exact Slugs for WP-CLI

```bash
# Install and activate in one pass
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp plugin install \
  --allow-root \
  rank-math-seo \
  fluentform \
  temporary-login-without-password \
  --activate
```

Notes:
- `rank-math-seo` — free version, full schema/sitemap/meta capability
- `fluentform` — free version, handles estimate form + photo upload field
- `temporary-login-without-password` — magic login link for client demo access
- `google-site-kit` — optional (requires real GSC/GA4 property; install but don't configure in demo)
- ShortPixel, UpdraftPlus, Wordfence — describe in proposal; skip install for demo (no API keys)

Generate magic login link after installing temporary-login-without-password:
```bash
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp tlwp create --allow-root \
  --email="demo@marylanddrivewayrestore.com" \
  --role="administrator" \
  --expiry="3 days" \
  --redirect="https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/maryland-driveway-restore/wp-admin/"
```
Save the printed URL. Include in proposal cover letter: "Click here to log in and explore the dashboard — link expires in 3 days."

