## 7. Custom Theme — mdr-theme (design-system faithful)

Create theme at `data/runner-workspace/mdr-wp/mdr-theme/`. Volume-mounted into container at `/var/www/html/wp-content/themes/mdr-theme`.

**style.css** (header only — WP theme identifier):
```css
/*
Theme Name: MDR Theme
Theme URI: https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/maryland-driveway-restore
Description: Custom theme for Maryland Driveway Restore demo
Version: 1.0
*/
```

**functions.php** — critical inclusions:
```php
<?php
function mdr_enqueue() {
    wp_enqueue_style('google-fonts', 'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap', [], null);
    wp_enqueue_style('mdr-style', get_template_directory_uri() . '/assets/css/main.css', [], '1.0');
    wp_enqueue_script('img-comparison-slider', 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/img-comparison-slider@8/dist/index.js', [], null, true);
    wp_enqueue_script('mdr-main', get_template_directory_uri() . '/assets/js/main.js', [], '1.0', true);
}
add_action('wp_enqueue_scripts', 'mdr_enqueue');

// Register nav menus
register_nav_menus(['primary' => 'Primary Menu', 'footer' => 'Footer Menu']);

// Add theme support
add_theme_support('title-tag');
add_theme_support('post-thumbnails');
add_theme_support('html5', ['search-form', 'comment-form', 'gallery', 'caption']);
add_theme_support('custom-logo');

// JSON-LD schema output in <head>
function mdr_schema_localbusiness() {
    if (!is_front_page() && !is_page()) return;
    $schema = [
        "@context" => "https://schema.org",
        "@type" => "HomeAndConstructionBusiness",
        "name" => "Maryland Driveway Restore",
        "url" => "https://api.michaelwegter.com/demos/maryland-driveway-restore",
        "telephone" => "+14105550100",
        "address" => [
            "@type" => "PostalAddress",
            "streetAddress" => "Annapolis, MD",
            "addressLocality" => "Annapolis",
            "addressRegion" => "MD",
            "postalCode" => "21401",
            "addressCountry" => "US"
        ],
        "areaServed" => ["Anne Arundel County", "Baltimore", "Howard County", "Prince George's County", "Montgomery County"],
        "aggregateRating" => [
            "@type" => "AggregateRating",
            "ratingValue" => "4.9",
            "reviewCount" => "47"
        ],
        "priceRange" => "\$\$"
    ];
    echo '<script type="application/ld+json">' . json_encode($schema, JSON_PRETTY_PRINT | JSON_UNESCAPED_SLASHES) . '</script>' . "\n";
}
add_action('wp_head', 'mdr_schema_localbusiness');
?>
```

