## 8. Page Creation (WP-CLI — all 9 pages)

```bash
# Delete default WP pages first
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post delete --allow-root $(docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post list --allow-root --post_type=page --format=ids) --force

# Create all pages with slugs
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="Home" --post_name="home" --page-template="front-page.php"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="Driveway Restoration" --post_name="driveway-restoration"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="Pricing" --post_name="pricing"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="Gallery" --post_name="gallery"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="About" --post_name="about"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="FAQ" --post_name="faq"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="Contact / Free Estimate" --post_name="contact"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="Service Areas" --post_name="service-areas"
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post create --allow-root --post_type=page --post_status=publish --post_title="Free Estimate" --post_name="free-estimate"

# Set homepage to static front page
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp option update --allow-root show_on_front page
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp option update --allow-root page_on_front $(docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp post list --allow-root --post_type=page --post_name=home --format=ids)

# Set permalink structure (clean URLs)
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp rewrite structure --allow-root '/%postname%/' --hard
docker exec --user www-data mdr-wordpress wp rewrite flush --allow-root --hard
```

